Name: SolaScriptura
Version: 0.1.2
Summary: A cross-platform interactive Bible reader for the terminal
Home-page: https://github.com/glitchassassin/sola-scriptura
Author: Jon Winsley
Author-email: jon.winsley@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: Bible Reader
        ------------
        
        This is a Python-based (and hence cross-platform) command-line Bible reader.
        
        Install with pip::
        
            pip install solascriptura
        
        And execute from the command line:
        
            solascriptura
Keywords: bible reader interactive terminal
